@PROCESSES
component-import: categories → compositions/templates import named exports
styling-flow: tokens.ts → per-category component uses colors/fonts/glow/springs → composed into scenes

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: styles/tokens (universal) | hooks/* (animation hooks)
external: remotion (useCurrentFrame, spring, interpolate, AbsoluteFill, Sequence, Img, Video)

@STANDARDS
- Every component imports brand values from styles/tokens
- Animated components use useCurrentFrame + spring/interpolate
- Props follow pattern: { ...data, style?: CSSProperties }
- Default export NOT used — named exports only
- Components are pure (no effects beyond Remotion hooks)
- No Tailwind — inline styles only
- Component filename = exported name (PascalCase)
